{"html":"<div class=\"hypothesis-box\"><div class=\"hypothesis-box-header\">仮説 #1</div><div class=\"hypothesis-meta-text\">基づくキーワード: 生物多様性の損失、環境に対する配慮</div><div class=\"hypothesis-box-body\"><div class=\"hypothesis-action-bar\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hypothesis-action-button add-node-button\">ノード追加</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"hypothesis-action-button scamper-button\">仮説を発散</button></div><textarea class=\"hypothesis-text\" placeholder=\"ここに仮説を入力\" data-last-logged-value=\"周辺の環境に生息する生物多様性は損なわれないか\" data-logging-bound=\"true\" data-has-action-bar=\"true\">周辺の環境に生息する生物多様性は損なわれないか</textarea></div><div class=\"hypothesis-controls\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hypothesis-delete-btn\">削除</button></div></div><div class=\"hypothesis-box\"><div class=\"hypothesis-box-header\">仮説 #2</div><div class=\"hypothesis-meta-text\">基づくキーワード: 技術、エネルギー効率</div><div class=\"hypothesis-box-body\"><div class=\"hypothesis-action-bar\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hypothesis-action-button add-node-button\">ノード追加</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"hypothesis-action-button scamper-button\">仮説を発散</button></div><textarea class=\"hypothesis-text\" placeholder=\"ここに仮説を入力\" data-last-logged-value=\"\" data-logging-bound=\"true\" data-has-action-bar=\"true\">エネルギー効率の高さについて考える</textarea></div><div class=\"hypothesis-controls\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hypothesis-delete-btn\">削除</button></div></div><div class=\"hypothesis-box\"><div class=\"hypothesis-box-header\">仮説 #3</div><div class=\"hypothesis-meta-text\">基づくキーワード: 廃棄物処理、持続可能なエネルギー</div><div class=\"hypothesis-box-body\"><div class=\"hypothesis-action-bar\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hypothesis-action-button add-node-button\">ノード追加</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"hypothesis-action-button scamper-button\">仮説を発散</button></div><textarea class=\"hypothesis-text\" placeholder=\"ここに仮説を入力\" data-last-logged-value=\"エネルギーを創出する上で，廃棄物は出るかについて考える\" data-logging-bound=\"true\" data-has-action-bar=\"true\">エネルギーを創出する上で，廃棄物は出るかについて考える</textarea></div><div class=\"hypothesis-controls\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hypothesis-delete-btn\">削除</button></div></div><div class=\"hypothesis-box\"><div class=\"hypothesis-box-header\">仮説 #4</div><div class=\"hypothesis-meta-text\">基づくキーワード: 安全性、危険物管理</div><div class=\"hypothesis-box-body\"><div class=\"hypothesis-action-bar\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hypothesis-action-button add-node-button\">ノード追加</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"hypothesis-action-button scamper-button\">仮説を発散</button></div><textarea class=\"hypothesis-text\" placeholder=\"ここに仮説を入力\" data-last-logged-value=\"人体に害をもたらすような物質は出ないか\" data-logging-bound=\"true\" data-has-action-bar=\"true\">人体に害をもたらすような物質は出ないか</textarea></div><div class=\"hypothesis-controls\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hypothesis-delete-btn\">削除</button></div></div><div class=\"hypothesis-box\"><div class=\"hypothesis-box-header\">仮説 #5</div><div class=\"hypothesis-meta-text\">基づくキーワード: 健康リスク、安全性</div><div class=\"hypothesis-box-body\"><div class=\"hypothesis-action-bar\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hypothesis-action-button add-node-button\">ノード追加</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"hypothesis-action-button scamper-button\">仮説を発散</button></div><textarea class=\"hypothesis-text\" placeholder=\"ここに仮説を入力\" data-last-logged-value=\"使い続けることで，周辺の住民に対し健康面でのリスクを負わせかねないか\" data-logging-bound=\"true\" data-has-action-bar=\"true\">使い続けることで，周辺の住民に対し健康面でのリスクを負わせかねないか</textarea></div><div class=\"hypothesis-controls\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hypothesis-delete-btn\">削除</button></div></div><div class=\"hypothesis-box\"><div class=\"hypothesis-box-header\">仮説 #6</div><div class=\"hypothesis-meta-text\">基づくキーワード: 耐久性について、故障率</div><div class=\"hypothesis-box-body\"><div class=\"hypothesis-action-bar\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hypothesis-action-button add-node-button\">ノード追加</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"hypothesis-action-button scamper-button\">仮説を発散</button></div><textarea class=\"hypothesis-text\" placeholder=\"ここに仮説を入力\" data-last-logged-value=\"故障率調査を行う\" data-logging-bound=\"true\" data-has-action-bar=\"true\">故障率調査を行う\n</textarea></div><div class=\"hypothesis-controls\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hypothesis-delete-btn\">削除</button></div></div><div class=\"hypothesis-box\"><div class=\"hypothesis-box-header\">仮説 #7</div><div class=\"hypothesis-meta-text\">基づくキーワード: 耐久性について、劣化</div><div class=\"hypothesis-box-body\"><div class=\"hypothesis-action-bar\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hypothesis-action-button add-node-button\">ノード追加</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"hypothesis-action-button scamper-button\">仮説を発散</button></div><textarea class=\"hypothesis-text\" placeholder=\"ここに仮説を入力\" data-last-logged-value=\"作成したシステムはどれほどの期間安全に使用できそうか\" data-logging-bound=\"true\" data-has-action-bar=\"true\">作成したシステムはどれほどの期間安全に使用できそうか</textarea></div><div class=\"hypothesis-controls\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hypothesis-delete-btn\">削除</button></div></div><div class=\"hypothesis-box\"><div class=\"hypothesis-box-header\">仮説 #8</div><div class=\"hypothesis-meta-text\">基づくキーワード: 蓄電可能か、エネルギー損失</div><div class=\"hypothesis-box-body\"><div class=\"hypothesis-action-bar\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hypothesis-action-button add-node-button\">ノード追加</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"hypothesis-action-button scamper-button\">仮説を発散</button></div><textarea class=\"hypothesis-text\" placeholder=\"ここに仮説を入力\" data-last-logged-value=\"\" data-logging-bound=\"true\" data-has-action-bar=\"true\"></textarea></div><div class=\"hypothesis-controls\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hypothesis-delete-btn\">削除</button></div></div>"}